_sText:
A small GG map made for my clan the Christian Crew, though I would be happy to let anyone else use it on their servers. If you would like it to be on your servers I would be more than happy to edit it to your liking (advertisment and such, seeing as I have stuff for CC on this map). 

There are 4 secret passageways on this map.  It comes with the standard 32 player slots. 

This map has been said to "look like a classic" so I hope you feel the same way and put it on your servers. :D  Thanks Chizbone for doing the NAV file :D

There is now a buyzone.


----------EDIT-------------

I had the wrong BSP for it, but now I changed it. So if you DL'ed it and it has errors near the spawn DL it again. Sorry for the inconvenience
